        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 12 at 7:30PM EDT until August 12 at 8:00PM EDT by NWS Grand Rapids MI</headline>
        <description>At 730 PM EDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 7 miles northwest of
Union City, or 10 miles south of Battle Creek, moving northeast at 40
mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Battle Creek...        Pine Creek...
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
